snippet.title: Best VGM 878 - Thunder Spirits - Hunger Made Them Desperate
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Thunder Spirits (1991)
Hunger Made Them Desperate
Tomomi Ootani & Toshiharu Yamanishi
